// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0073 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bd964d1b-0b38-5108-ae4b-8086eea18b48

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
